behavior load_bowls_and_plates(dishwasher:item):

            # Load all bowls and plates found around the dishwasher into the dishwasher
            if is_bowl(o) or is_plate(o) and close(o, dishwasher):
                achieve inside(o, dishwasher)

        load_bowls_and_plates(dishwasher)

behavior load_dishwasher(o:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(o, dishwasher)

behavior start_dishwasher(dishwasher:item, soap:item):
    body:
        put_dish_soap_in_dishwasher(soap, dishwasher)
        achieve closed(dishwasher)
        achieve is_on(dishwasher)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher) and id[dishwasher] == 1001
        bind soap: item where:
            is_soap(soap)
        
        foreach o: item:
            if (is_plate(o) or is_bowl(o)) and close(o, dishwasher):
                load_dishwasher(o, dishwasher)
        
        start_dishwasher(dishwasher, soap)
